1237 // entity events are for effects that take place reletive
1238 // to an existing entities origin. Very network efficient.

1241 // will be incremented with each change in the event so
1242 // that an identical event started twice in a row can
1243 // be distinguished. And off the value with ~EV_EVENT_BITS
1244 // to retrieve the actual event number
1245 #define EV_EVENT_BIT1 0x00000100
1246 #define EV_EVENT_BIT2 0x00000200
1247 #define EV_EVENT_BITS (EV_EVENT_BIT1 | EV_EVENT_BIT2)
